'''Mohammad Ghorbani''' ({{langx|fa|محمد قربانی}}; born 7 October 2001) is an [[Iran]]ian professional [[association football|footballer]] who plays for Emirati club [[Al Wahda FC|Al Wahda]] and the [[Iran national football team|Iran national team]].

==Club career==
===Nassaji Mazandaran===
He made his debut for [[F.C. Nassaji Mazandaran|Nassaji Mazandaran]] in the first fixtures of [[2021–22 Persian Gulf Pro League]] against [[Fajr Sepasi Shiraz F.C.|Fajr Sepasi Shiraz]].<ref>[https://www.varzesh3.com/news/1786496/%DA%AF%D8%B2%D8%A7%D8%B1%D8%B4-%D8%A8%D8%A7%D8%B2%DB%8C-%D9%86%D8%B3%D8%A7%D8%AC%DB%8C-%D9%85%D8%A7%D8%B2%D9%86%D8%AF%D8%B1%D8%A7%D9%86-%D9%88-%D9%81%D8%AC%D8%B1-%D8%B3%D9%BE%D8%A7%D8%B3%DB%8C-1400-07-27 نساجی 1-0 فجرسپاسی؛الهامی گام نخست را محکم برداشت]</ref>

===Orenburg===
On 21 February 2024, Ghorbani joined [[Russian Premier League]] club [[FC Orenburg|Orenburg]].<ref>{{cite web|publisher=FC Orenburg|url=https://fcorenburg.ru/news/novosti-osnovy/mohammad-gorbani-v-fk-orenburg.html|title=Мохаммад Горбани в ФК "Оренбург"|date=21 February 2024|language=ru}}</ref>

===Al Wahda===
On 5 February 2025, Ghorbani moved to [[Al Wahda FC|Al Wahda]] in the United Arab Emirates.<ref>{{cite web|publisher=FC Orenburg|url=https://fcorenburg.ru/news/novosti-osnovy/mohammad-gorbani-perehodit-v-emiratskij-al-vahda.html|title=Мохаммад Горбани переходит в эмиратский "Аль-Вахда"|date=5 February 2025|language=ru}}</ref>

==International career==
Ghorbani was called up for the first time to the senior [[Iran national football team|Iran national team]] in November 2022 for a friendly against Nicaragua, but remained on the bench in the game.<ref>{{cite web|publisher=ESPN|url=https://www.espn.com/soccer/match/_/gameId/655819/nicaragua-iran|title=Iran v Nicaragua game report|date=10 November 2022}}</ref>

Ghorbani made his debut on 26 March 2024 in a [[2026 FIFA World Cup qualification – AFC second round|World Cup qualifier]] against [[Turkmenistan national football team|Turkmenistan]].<ref>{{cite web|publisher=ESPN|url=https://www.espn.co.uk/football/match/_/gameId/687434/iran-turkmenistan|title=Turkmenistan v Iran game report|date=26 March 2024}}</ref>

